{"tid":2237273,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陳皓桓證實涉協助逃犯罪","createTime":"2020-10-10T06:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T06:35:08.000Z","uid":211994,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ecfe64b70ebad8e853af78473309e590c172ed","tid":2237273,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:23:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553968-20201010.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553968-20201010.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDJggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=b76d52e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553968-20201010.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=89030f64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553968-20201010.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n警方今日清晨在九龍及新界拘捕4男5女，涉嫌干犯協助逃犯罪，懷疑9人早前協助12名港人非法越境。<br />\n<br />\n社民連成員陳皓桓證實，其中一名被捕人士是立法會前議員梁國雄的前助理唐婉清。陳皓桓說，唐婉清被指參與窩藏罪犯，現正在旺角警署，並已獲安排與律師見面，暫時未知能否保釋。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，9名被捕人士的角色，包括船主、為12人提供資金和安排偷渡前的交通住宿，以及安排他們到台灣後的生活；又說不排除會有更多人被捕。"},{"pid":"5409987387d8d1888e3fe64a8096a00a6afbefac","tid":2237273,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:23:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d871c62778378d85d9f38dde02acea00c9278fc5","tid":2237273,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:24:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f59d7f225ddd8da71fc3fb400b720109e659113d","tid":2237273,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:24:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2357c0078ceec6121facfca7e9495f676ab794f8","tid":2237273,"uid":8659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:24:58.000Z","msg":"個標題做乜鳩"},{"pid":"8f3cc3f872db17c6b44b02932e568c267be38362","tid":2237273,"uid":44180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"